// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2026-0029 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: f8821e91-2ec1-59b9-9c42-3e8d90769309

#event_simpleName=*
| (ImageFileName = *debian:12* OR ImageFileName = *debian:13* OR ImageFileName = *debian:14*)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
